{"tid":1708667,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"疑不滿黑衣人破壞起爭執 被火燒大叔命危","createTime":"2019-11-11T15:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T17:07:46.000Z","uid":259088,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"df14155f4d73dc92dd4f9afbfb8b097e339e6f21","tid":1708667,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2495000/2495227/111_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2495000%2F2495227%2F111_600.jpg&h=32f5e53c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3537998/org/784702d318783d2c0f7a7deadadb75b1.jpeg/fQpEcSRfVyQnHmjHYxk_qf1szPF02R-t4bKQneGykJ0?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3537998%2Forg%2F784702d318783d2c0f7a7deadadb75b1.jpeg%2FfQpEcSRfVyQnHmjHYxk_qf1szPF02R-t4bKQneGykJ0%3Fv%3Dw480&h=0cf2f927&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3537999/org/0f192225011bbf38c8f6b6333f2e828c.jpeg/QwygOHcU0FJgw2diN0p-PzTr3hFa13LeCtHuhArR7oQ?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3537999%2Forg%2F0f192225011bbf38c8f6b6333f2e828c.jpeg%2FQwygOHcU0FJgw2diN0p-PzTr3hFa13LeCtHuhArR7oQ%3Fv%3Dw480&h=d395f273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（網上截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山57歲男子遭蒙面黑衣男潑液體放火成「火人」　送往威爾斯醫院情況危殆<br />\n 社會 15:25 2019/11/11 <br />\n熱門秋冬湯水 貨櫃藏屍 牛下女高音 移民 晚間看地球 開心速遞 陳同佳案 消委會 抗癌新方向 兒童健康<br />\n網上流傳一段影片，一名男子疑因政見不同，與在場人士發生衝突，其後被蒙面黑衣人淋潑易燃液體並點火。（網上截圖）<br />\n<br />\n▲ 網上流傳一段影片，一名男子疑因政見不同，與在場人士發生衝突，其後被蒙面黑衣人淋潑易燃液體並點火。（網上截圖）<br />\n<br />\n反修例風波持續，網上流傳一段影片，一名男子疑因政見不同，與在場聚集人士衝突，其後被蒙面黑衣男子上前潑易燃液體並點火，該名男子頓成「火人」，其後由救護車被送往威爾斯醫院接受治理，目前情況危殆。據了解，該男子的雙手、胸部、面部被燒傷，屬二級燒傷，於深切治療部留醫。<br />\n<br />\n從網上片段顯示，事件發生在馬鞍山海柏花園一條行人天橋，一名身穿綠色上衣的男子，疑因政見問題與在場人士爭吵，頭部受傷流血，亦發生發生肢體衝突。<br />\n<br />\n爭吵期間，綠衣男指著在場人士並大罵，其言論引起在場其他人士不滿，有人出言反駁，雙方發生激烈口角。<br />\n<br />\n此時，有蒙面黑衣男子上前向綠衣男淋潑液體並點火，綠衣男全身著火，他向後逃跑並脫下上衣。該名男子皮膚被燒傷，全身燻黑，坐在地上等待救援。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，初步了解事發在今日中午12許，案件暫列作襲擊，交由新界南重案組跟進。醫管局表示，截至下午2時半，該名57歲男傷者目前在威爾斯醫院留醫，目前情況危殆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2495227/%E9%A6%AC%E9%9E%8D%E5%B1%B157%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E9%81%AD%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E7%94%B7%E6%BD%91%E6%B6%B2%E9%AB%94%E6%94%BE%E7%81%AB%E6%88%90%E3%80%8C%E7%81%AB%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E9%80%81%E5%BE%80%E5%A8%81%E7%88%BE%E6%96%AF%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E5%8D%B1%E6%AE%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2495227%2F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%259E%258D%25E5%25B1%25B157%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%25BD%2591%25E6%25B6%25B2%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%2594%25BE%25E7%2581%25AB%25E6%2588%2590%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%2581%25AB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E3%2580%258D%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%2580%2581%25E5%25BE%2580%25E5%25A8%2581%25E7%2588%25BE%25E6%2596%25AF%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B3%2581%25E5%258D%25B1%25E6%25AE%2586&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQdAsgxU2M8QNPxyQAqp636I%3D&h=5a6b7e82\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2495227/%E9%A6%AC%E9%9E%8D%E5%B1%B157%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E9%81%AD%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E9%BB%91%E8%A1%A3%E7%94%B7%E6%BD%91%E6%B6%B2%E9%AB%94%E6%94%BE%E7%81%AB%E6%88%90%E3%80%8C%E7%81%AB%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E9%80%81%E5%BE%80%E5%A8%81%E7%88%BE%E6%96%AF%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E5%8D%B1%E6%AE%86</a>"},{"pid":"cc87056798e78ff363ede921d225daa88011bf92","tid":1708667,"uid":263310,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:55:50.000Z","msg":"叔一燒"},{"pid":"36856a6f3fb114e223992cbc82f68c3fccd763fb","tid":1708667,"uid":108337,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:00:56.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣叫命危 收皮啦"},{"pid":"42